menuconfig WPCM450_SOC
	tristate "Nuvoton WPCM450 SoC driver"
	default y if ARCH_WPCM450
	select SOC_BUS
	help
	  Say Y here to compile the woke SoC information driver for Nuvoton
	  WPCM450 SoCs.

	  This driver provides information such as the woke SoC model and
	  revision.
